            <div className="col-md-12">
              <div className="section-title" style={{ textAlign: "center" }}>
                <h2 className="title" style={{ animation: "none" }}>
                  Achievements
                </h2>
                <p>
                  The success of Radhika Jeweltech Limited is evident in the
                  Awards received for excellence and has proved to be above the
                  rest.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div className="row mbn-30">
            <div className="col-lg-4 col-md-4">
              <div className="single-choose-item text-center mb-30">
                <i className="fa fa-trophy" />
                <h4>2nd highest tax payer</h4>
                <p>
                  Radhika Jewellers was declared as
                  <span style={{ fontWeight: 700 }}>
                    2nd highest tax payer in Gujarat state
                  </span>
                  , In the{" "}
                  <span style={{ fontWeight: "bold" }}> year 2014.</span>
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div className="col-lg-4 col-md-4">
              <div className="single-choose-item text-center mb-30">
                <i className="fa fa-trophy" />
                <h4>Best Retail Jewellery showroom-west</h4>
                <p>
                  Radhika Jewellers has won an award of excellence for the
                  <span style={{ fontWeight: 700 }}>
                    Best Retail Jewellery showroom-west
                  </span>
                  , Awarded by
                  <span style={{ fontWeight: 700 }}>
                    ‘Gem &amp; Jewellery Trade Council Of India’
                  </span>
                  on ,
                  <span style={{ fontWeight: "bold" }}>27th December 2014</span>
                  .
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div className="col-lg-4 col-md-4">
              <div className="single-choose-item text-center mb-30">
                <i className="fa fa-trophy" />
                <h4>social activity</h4>
